{"tid":1613820,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黎智英: 不會對勇武抗爭者割席","createTime":"2019-10-02T15:40:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T11:01:41.000Z","uid":134071,"like":515,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"9646b6e8f1db81fc90bba45834cb763b5d966723","tid":1613820,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:40:17.000Z","msg":"Fox news訪問<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20191002/60109569\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191002%2F60109569&d=Bbcm6JBZsUbsJrWfDZmHX%2BxpY9ERoCMedVnvBBvIoB8%3D&h=89e3cabe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191002%2F60109569&h=e77bd872\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20191002/60109569</a><br />\n<br />\n 2019年10月02日<br />\n【逆權運動】黎智英接受霍士訪問 指港人無懼北京恫嚇 不會與抗爭者割席 <br />\n<br />\n壹傳媒集團創辦人<strong>黎智英美國時間周三早上（香港時間周三晚上）接受美國霍士新聞《Mornings with Maria》越洋訪問</strong>，他表示中共雖然在10.1閱兵，但爭取民主自由的港人不會被嚇倒，<strong>他又指示威雖然出現了暴力的情況，但年長一代不會與他們割席。</strong><br />\n<br />\n黎智英表示，《基本法》賦予港人雙普選的權利，港人現時只是爭取應有的權利。面對中共在10.1閱兵，黎智英指北京不會成功恫嚇港人，因為港人非常堅決爭取雙普選，保持香港原有的生活方式，不會讓他們拿走港人的自由，或侵蝕香港的法治或人權。黎智英指，除了香港，年輕人無處可去，他們只能爭取自己的和平，香港的年輕人不能接受中國的生活方式。<br />\n<br />\n黎智英承認，目前大部份抗爭者都是年輕人，而年長一代在過往的三十年抗爭，未能為年輕人爭取任何東西，現時年輕人用自己的方式抗爭，我們（年長一代）無話可說，只能支持他們。<br />\n<br />\n黎智英預計，一名18歲學生在10.1中槍後，示威會變得更激烈以回應警方濫暴，雖然他不希望年輕人再進一步把武力升級，擔心會因此失去了道德高地，<strong>但黎智英指出，他們即使這樣做，我們仍有責任與他們一起，因為大家是團結一起的。</strong><br />\n<br />\n美國霍士新聞"},{"pid":"baa97fe7ee5513f34409ffba3da661551e350bfb","tid":1613820,"uid":134071,"like":58,"dislike":0,"score":58,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:40:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190709/large/1562644999_586f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190709%2Flarge%2F1562644999_586f.jpg&h=928e33c2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0846c8c6ce06fb12a132a17d58580172e777d7bd","tid":1613820,"uid":134071,"like":54,"dislike":0,"score":54,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:41:47.000Z","msg":"對住美媒Fox news話唔會割席<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b640c92178349a7ac588d5019fe4d1a2986a769","tid":1613820,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:42:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5edba54b4c65b83a6d6f9f0d247996d7976ac27","tid":1613820,"uid":254581,"like":19,"dislike":3,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"0846c8c6ce06fb12a132a17d58580172e777d7bd","tid":1613820,"uid":134071,"like":54,"dislike":0,"score":54,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:41:47.000Z","msg":"對住美媒Fox news話唔會割席<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:43:35.000Z","msg":"美帝落order<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f32be9d4b37f394d89e3d49a8d5c219479baf76","tid":1613820,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:44:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d16aa40c13429f746655b37827f2f36874110dd","tid":1613820,"uid":66686,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:44:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>We shall never surrender</strong></span>"},{"pid":"f882bf72bd5fffcced1832c7999743e73378690b","tid":1613820,"uid":134071,"like":0,"disli