n>，大家一齊cover勇武，而唔係質疑佢地。<br />\n<br />\n（我屌你地老味，班死黑警開真槍死都拗返生，勇武做少少嘢就阿之阿左，睇到有人開始質疑勇武真係急撚到喊出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）"},{"pid":"344f391f56500a1b8464bfde4d865f921e4a981c","tid":1613820,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"78289af72e3ff3f63ab1e742eb1bc336d343838f","tid":1613820,"uid":95138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3358ef38e679e26298672156e3fd16f711adbfb0","tid":1613820,"uid":43041,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:45:50.000Z","msg":"割席英文系咩牙？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T16:11:08.000Z","msg":"正想問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T16:11:55.000Z","msg":"毛孟靜:<br />\n<br />\n割席的英文可以是 to distance oneself from someone or something ，與一些人或物保持距離、與之切割。<br />\n<br />\n用於政治：<br />\n‧The leader has recently distanced himself from the extremists in the party. 領袖最近與黨內的極端分子割席。<br />\n<br />\n用於商業：<br />\n‧The company has been trying to pretend to be environmentally friendly and has been distancing itself from its past connections to the oil industry. 公司企圖裝作環保，與過去的石油業務聯繫切割。<br />\n<br />\n用於日常生活：<br />\n‧You have to stay in touch. You cannot distance yourself from reality. 你要保持聯繫，不可與現實切割。<br />\n<br />\n‧We should all live a simple life and distance ourselves from consumerism. 我們都應該生活簡約，與消費主義切割。<br />\n<br />\n上面的句子，若不用 distance，可以改作 dissociate，意思基本上一樣。<br />\n<br />\n割席亦可說 to sever ties，但多用於斷絕關係：<br />\n<br />\n‧The two countries sever ties after a huge diplomatic row. 兩國於一場外交大爭議後，斷絕邦交。<br />\n<br />\n另有 split up，就多指個人關係：<br />\n‧His parents have decided to split up. 他的父母決定分手了。<br />\n‧The group has refused to split up. 團體拒絕分散。這句的含意，不就是「不分化」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E8%8B%B1%E6%96%87/article/20190909/s00017/1567967872741\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E8%258B%25B1%25E6%2596%2587%2Farticle%2F20190909%2Fs00017%2F1567967872741&d=Bbcm6JBZsUbsJrWfDZmHX%2BxpY9ERoCMedVnvBBvIoB8%3D&h=89b18f7f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E8%258B%25B1%25E6%2596%2587%2Farticle%2F20190909%2Fs00017%2F1567967872741&h=a47cc877\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E8%8B%B1%E6%96%87/article/20190909/s00017/1567967872741</a>"},{"pid":"8b70ef720eca6abb9b53f6ef8c694006a5b9d9cc","tid":1613820,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T16:13:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6c7dc9d4f3c5986fce2e2d94cd869c1de8b8b89","tid":1613820,"uid":83,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T16:14:25.000Z","msg":"啫係美國話唔割<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bd119e4691626fca0cdbecfca4ed739d15c1acc","tid":1613820,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T16:17:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cf9177721aee428422767efafab5a0b808b5324b","tid":1613820,"uid":237209,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"6e800413aea7ff8d5fbbbe0f01151c7ec37313c2","tid":1613820,"uid":134071,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"quote":{"pid":"3358ef38e679e26298672156e3fd16f711adbfb0","tid":1613820,"uid":43041,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:45:50.000Z","msg":"割席英文系咩牙？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:52:30.000Z","msg":"毛孟靜: <br />\n<br />\n割席的英文可以是 to distance oneself from someone or something ，與一些人或物保持距離、與之切割。<br />\n<br />\n用於政治：<br />\n‧The leader has recently distanced himself from the extremists in the party. 領袖最近與黨內的極端分子割席。<br />\n<br />\n用於商業：<br />\n‧The company has been trying to pretend to be environmentally friendly and has been distancing itself from its past connections to the oil industry. 公司企圖裝作環保，與過去的石油業務聯繫切割。<br />\n<br />\n用於日常生活：<br />\n‧You have to stay in touch. You cannot distance yourself from reality. 你要保持聯繫，不可與現實切割。<br />\n<br />\n‧We should all live a simple life and distance ourselves from consumerism. 我們都應該生活簡約，與消費主義切割。<br />\n<br />\n上面的句子，若不用 distance，可以改作 dissociate，意思基本上一樣。<br />\n<br />\n割席亦可說 to sever ties，但多用於斷絕關係：<br />\n<br />\n‧The two countries sever ties after a huge diplomatic row. 兩國於一場外交大爭議後，斷絕邦交。<br />\n<br />\n另有 split up，就多指個人關係：<br />\n‧His parents have decided to split up. 他的父母決定分手了。<br />\n‧The group has refused to split up. 團體拒絕分散。<strong>這句的含意，不就是「不分化」。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E8%8B%B1%E6%96%87/article/20190909/s00017/1567967872741\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E8%258B%25B1%25E6%2596%2587%2Farticle%2F20190909%2Fs00017%2F1567967872741&d=Bbcm6JBZsUbsJrWfDZmHX%2BxpY9ERoCMedVnvBBvIoB8%3D&h=89b18f7f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E8%258B%25B1%25E6%2596%2587%2Farticle%2F20190909%2Fs00017%2F1567967872741&h=a47cc877\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E8%8B%B1%E6%96%87/article/20190909/s00017/1567967872741</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T16:21:11.000Z","msg":"契媽好勁<br />\n希望下個sem reg到佢嘅堂"},{"pid":"f08bed5f2228f1a27c7f7004e0cefe4f6f8aee48","tid":1613820,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T16:23:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be5f2cde7ebe925e367bf260f1d9aa78148e5d4e","tid":1613820,"uid":55257,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T16:23:45.000Z","msg":"撐你呀今次"},{"pid":"11bbd